<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FoodShare - Share Food, Share Love</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hero-section">
        <h1>Share more, waste less</h1>
        <p>We make it easy to share your extra food with your community. Whether you're an individual, a business, or a nonprofit, we have a solution for you.</p>
        <a href="/register" class="nav-button primary">Get started</a>
    </div>

    <div class="features-section">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">📝</div>
            <h3>Post Food</h3>
            <p>In just a few taps, let us know what you have to share.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🔍</div>
            <h3>Claim Food</h3>
            <p>Find food near you that's available for pickup. You can filter by distance and food type.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🚚</div>
            <h3>Deliver Food</h3>
            <p>Help get food from donors to recipients. You can earn points for each delivery.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 